# Phone UI ("폰 속의 폰")

Component hierarchy:

```
PhoneFrame
└── HomeScreen (app icons, notifications)
    ├── ChatApp
    ├── SMSApp
    ├── CallScreen
    ├── BankApp
    ├── InstagramDM
    └── DatingApp
```

## Design

- Outer: desktop browser canvas; inner: ~390×844px phone bezel
- Apps are **generic renderers** — same component serves all 7 scenarios
- Props: `messages`, `options`, `onSelect`, `timerSeconds`, `isStreaming`
- Realistic app chrome (status bar, nav) — not "game UI" aesthetic

## Streaming UX

- Show typing indicator while LLM streams
- Messages append with Framer Motion `AnimatePresence`
- Timer overlay when `timer_seconds` set on node

## Accessibility

- Text input fallback always visible (mic optional)
- Sufficient contrast for warning/danger states
